    <owl:AnnotationProperty rdf:about="https://ontology.staging.domus.usherbrooke.ca/MAO#definition">
        <rdfs:label>definition</rdfs:label>
        <definition>The official definition, explaining the meaning of a class or property. Shall be Aristotelian, formalized and normalized. Can be augmented with colloquial definitions.</definition>
